{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|p}} – a kind of agricultural tool used for tilling the fields and removing weeds ({{zh-ref|Guo, 1931}}; {{zh-ref|Qiu, 1992}}), possibly made of a kind of large clam {{och-l|蜃}} ({{zh-ref|Guo, 1931}}).

Alternatively, it could be a {{liushu|p|nocap=1}} of a person holding onto a cliff – original character of {{och-l|振|to hold up}} ({{zh-ref|Shang, 1983}}).

